               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1r" to="192v">1r-192v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="acephalous apodous lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s38IHA">قران, First half (ǧuz’ 1-15)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>الم ذلك الكتاب لا ريب فيه هدى للمتقين</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#192r">-192r</locus>وبرا [بوالديه] ولم يكن  جبارا عصيا , وسلام عليه يوم  <note>The lower left corner of the page is torn loose and appears attached to the lower pasteboard.</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>Fol. 1 is upside down. The text begins on fol. 1v and continues to fol. 1r. Fol. 192 is turned front to back: sūra 19 starting on fol. 192v continues to fol 192r. The text begins from the beginning of sūra 2 to the first words of verse 19:15 (fol. 192r). Lacuna between fols 191 and 192. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
